name: Astronaut Backrooms
description:
I used this for a machinima I made it.

You can check it out here:

Backrooms Idea. I learned 3d game development just for this.

Scrapped Game. No Sounds. No Start Menu. No Quit Menu. Windowed. Backrooms Concept. With used assets from others.

Controls:

WASD - move

Mouse - look

Space - infinite double jumps

Esc- will stop the game forever so you can exit
